 Kat Von D赢得了Miles Davis Tattoo的版权诉讼https://www.nme.com/news/music/kat-von-d-wins-copyright-lawsuit-over-miles-davis-tattoo-3578610?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kat-von-d-wins-版权法律 - 戴维斯纹身Liberty DunworthMon, 29 Jan 2024 11:03:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsJazzhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3578610 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯特·冯·D和迈尔斯·戴维斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该诉讼在2021年被摄影师起诉后起出</p><p>凯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kat-von-d-wins-copyright-lawsuit-over-miles-davis-tattoo-3578610">·冯（Kat von d）赢得了迈尔斯·戴维斯（Miles Davis）纹身的版权诉讼，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯特·冯·D和迈尔斯·戴维斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kat-Von-D-Miles-Davis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>凯特·冯·D（Kat von d）赢得了几年前<a href="/artists/miles-davis">戴维斯（Davis）</a>纹身英里的版权诉讼。</p><p>这位备受瞩目的纹身艺术家和音乐家在2021年面临侵犯版权侵权的指控，当时她被摄影师杰弗里·塞德利克（Jeffrey Sedlik）起诉，因为她纹身了标志性的爵士艺术家迈尔斯·戴维斯（Miles Davis）的肖像。</p><p>根据诉讼，塞德利克（Sedlik）声称，冯·D（Von d）在2017年墨水的肖像构成了他1989年对音乐家拍摄的一张图像的版权侵犯，这是<em>爵士乐</em>杂志的封面故事的一部分。</p><p>现在，在诉讼首次提起诉讼后将近三年后，冯·D赢得了此案，并已清除了任何侵权指控。这是因为陪审团裁定照片的纹身繁殖并没有侵犯版权。</p><p>凯特·冯·D（Kat von D）的律师在星期五（1月26日）告诉<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/01/27/arts/kat-von-d-miles-davis-tattoo-copyright-trial.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a> 。 “陪审团花了两个小时才得出每个人从一开始就应该得出的相同结论：这里发生的事情不是侵权。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/BRzNjo2AfDK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.